<p>CHAPTER 41N - PARENTING ALLOWANCE - Benefit and non-benefit parenting allowance. See guideline 41N.6200.</p>
<p>As announced in the 1996-97 Budget, the Earnings Credit Scheme is to be abolished for all payments as of 20 March 1997.</p>
