<h2>Update 786G # Date 9 January 1997</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 28 - ASSETS - OVERVIEW AND ASSESSMENT - New chapter 28. See guidelines 28.000 to 28.6302.</p>
<p>The new chapter 28, on the overview and assessment of assets, replaces Part G of current chapter 27 (except for assessment of the principal home, which has been included in new chapter 29). It includes treatment of exempt assets, assessable assets, market value and hardship.</p>
<h2>Update 785G # Date 9 January 1997</h2>
